OL,3,CMPs call for urgent reform of
OL,4,CGovernment culture to make the UK 'fit
OL,5,Cfor future'
OL,7,FA Government committee has called for
OL,8,Fan "urgent reform" of Government
OL,9,Fculture to improve strategic decision
OL,10,Fmaking and make UK "fit for the
OL,11,Ffuture".
OL,13,FThe House of Commons Liaison
OL,14,FCommittee, made up of MPs who chair
OL,15,FCommons select committees, has
OL,16,Freleased a report detailing how the
OL,17,FGovernment can improve strategic
OL,18,Fthinking and future-proof decision
OL,19,Fmaking for generations to come.
