OL,3,CMPs call for urgent reform of
OL,4,CGovernment culture to make the UK 'fit
OL,5,Cfor future'
OL,7,FThe committee heard evidence that
OL,8,Fyounger generations are becoming
OL,9,F"detached from democracy" and are more
OL,10,Fopen to authoritarianism, with the
OL,11,Ffailure to address long-term issues
OL,12,Flike housing and climate change
OL,13,Fleading to a disengagement with the
OL,14,Fpolitical system.
