OL,3,CMPs call for urgent reform of
OL,4,CGovernment culture to make the UK 'fit
OL,5,Cfor future'
OL,7,FLiaison Committee chairman Sir Bernard
OL,8,FJenkin said: "Getting Parliament and
OL,9,Fgovernment to be more strategic than
OL,10,Fthey have been over the past 20 or 30
OL,11,Fyears is vital to restoring public
OL,12,Fconfidence in our entire democratic
OL,13,Fsystem, particularly among younger
OL,14,Fgenerations who will inherit the
OL,15,Fconsequences of what governments do
OL,16,Fnow.
OL,18,F"The next government should seize this
OL,19,Foffer from Parliament to support and
OL,20,Fscrutinise strategic thinking for the
OL,21,Ffuture."
OL,26,@pD@NOUzD@AOU}D@HO]
