OL,3,CMPs call for urgent reform of
OL,4,CGovernment culture to make the UK 'fit
OL,5,Cfor future'
OL,7,FThe report outlined that the next
OL,8,Fgovernment should set out its national
OL,9,Fstrategy to Parliament annually and
OL,10,Fdefine five or six "key strategic
OL,11,Fpriorities" which would be monitored
OL,12,Fand subject to an annual report to
OL,13,FParliament.
OL,15,FThe committee also recommended
OL,16,Fcreating a new select committee called
OL,17,Fthe Committee For The Future with a
OL,18,Fspecific focus on future generations
OL,19,Fwhich would hold ministers and
OL,20,Fofficials to account for the
OL,21,FGovernment's national strategy.
